n shows how an appreciation of the body’s intelligence will enrich all our lives.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aBody-mind centering. 0aMind and body. 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Neuroscience.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021597740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300215977423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300215977/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles